     H            Y.
     F** ALDR9P *********************************************
     F* PURGE DELETED RECS & ERR RECS FROM ALDPP9V          *
     F*  LEC                        2023.06.13              *
     F*******************************************************
     FALDPP9V UF  E           K        DISK
      *
     I           SDS
     I                                     *PROGRAM W#PGM
     I                                      244 253 W#WSID
     I                                      254 263 W#USER
     I                                      264 269 W#JBNO
      *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * MAINLINE                                           *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
      *
     C                     READ ALDPP9V                  50
     C   50                LEAVE
      *
     C           AVSKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C           AVOKNG    OREQ 'NG'
     C                     DELETALDPP9V1
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
      *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
